Tas all

1. Tell em tat ta nomb on ta closet hasbeen askin for em, then watch them go chek if not actually have a conversation
2. Throw a spagetti noodle at em n tell em its a snake
3. Turn on all ta t.v.s in ta house to cartoons.
4. Make 2 bowls of ice cream, 1 for u, n then put dogshit in ta otha n wait for ta fuka ta get hungry

These are it for now if ya can think of extra's feel free ta write a comment or im me.
